        <unitName xml:lang="en">kg</unitName>
        <comment xml:lang="en">There was no data available on process emissions to air for the methanesulfonic acid production. As approximation the air emissions occurring from the purge vent, the distillation vent and fugitive emission sources were estimated to 0.2% of the input of methane and sulfur trioxide.</comment>
